      "releaseNotes": "Bug Fixes:\n\nFixes to Italian translations\nChests screen now shows correct chest type\nChests screen now includes chests inside Farm buildings\n\nNew Features:\n\nSet time played\nClothing Store\nFurniture Store\nNew Rare Items\nRemove Unmoveable Items (incubators, mushroom boxes, etc.)\n\nUpdates item store organization:\n\nCraft Shop -> Animal Produce, Artisan Items, Craftables, Rare Goods\nFarm Shop -> Flowers & Foraged Items, Fruits & Vegetables\n\nItem stores now warn about immovable objects",
